<pb facs="1078678" n="1r"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Clarissimo atque Incomparabili
                        <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Johanni Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></salute></opener>
<p>Quoniam hac hebdomada responsum, uti sperabam,
                        <lb/>ad meas <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></choice> ultima pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teriti Augusti <rs key="B_1714-08-31_991170515019805501" type="letter">datas</rs><note type="editorial">Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Johann I Bernoulli, 31. August 1714.</note> non accepi,
                        <lb/>non abs re fore iudico unam adhuc ad te mittere epis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tolam adhoc ut si forte fortuna prim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> litter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>ad tuas non pervenerint manus, saltem h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c, quam etiam
                        <lb/>per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs> amandare decerno, perveniat.</p>
<p><choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimi</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Excell:<hi rend="sup">mi</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimi</expan></choice> D. D. Patavini Archilyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>i <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatores</rs>
<lb/>responsum a Te Vir Doctissime expectant, cupiuntque
                        <lb/>scire num sis derelicturus Patriam <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavinam</rs>
<lb/>Provinciam amplexurus salario annuo 1500 Thalerorum
                        <lb/>imperialium Tibi persoluto. Ego revera ipsis <choice><abbr>Nobiliss.<hi rend="sup">mis</hi></abbr><expan>Nobilissimis</expan></choice>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatoribus</rs> spem aliquam Tui obtinendi feci si
                        <lb/>annuatim persolvere velint 1500 Thaleros imperiales
                        <lb/>hoc est totidem uncias argenti; hancque spem deduxi
                        <lb/>ex <rs key="B_1714-07-18_991170515020205501" type="letter">humanissima tua epistola</rs><note type="editorial">Johann I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti vom 18. Juli 1714.</note> 18 Julii exarata, in qua
                        <lb/>scripsisti Vir Celeberrime Te ne quidem permotum
                        <lb/>iri oblat<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> summa minori quam 1500 Thalerorum impe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rialium hoc est totidem unciarum argenti. Salarium
                        <lb/>1500 Thalerorum imperialium quod petivisti Tibi exhi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bent, atque persolvent annuatim Amplissimi Patavini
                        <lb/>Archilyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>i <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatores</rs>: quare reliquum est ut Tu Vir
                        <lb/>Clarissime sine mora <rs key="B_1714-10-20_991170515019305501" type="letter">litteris tuis</rs><note type="editorial">Bernoulli gibt Antwort in seinem Brief vom 20. Oktober 1714. Dort bringt er vor, dass er eine andere Art Taler von höherem Wert gemeint hat, weshalb er die Berufung nach Padua im Unsicheren bleiben lässt.</note> iucundissimis me
                        <lb/>admonitum facias de tuo adventu, quem cum Proce<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1078679" n="1v"/>
<lb break="no"/>ribus<note type="editorial">Gemeint sind hier vermutlich adlige Venezianer aus dem Umfeld Michelottis.</note> meis multisque Viris doctis ipse exopto. Uti dice<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bam in <rs key="B_1714-08-31_991170515019805501" type="letter">pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedentibus meis</rs><note type="editorial">Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Johann I Bernoulli, 31. August 1714.</note> progressu temporis poteris
                        <lb/>substituere Agnatum Tuum Doctissimum <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaum</rs>
<lb/>si <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavina Urbs</rs> non arridebit: c<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m aer pata<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vinus optimus est, et temperamento tuo conducet;
                        <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Veneti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> fortasse non displicebunt vacationum tempo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re, quo cubiculum Domi me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sine expensis tibi sem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>per paratum erit. Stipendium oblatum 1500 Tha<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lerorum imperialium ne respuas rogo, et vocatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nibus tam honorificis ne relucteris deprecor saltem
                        <lb/>ne labores mei pro Vobis libentissime impensi eva<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dant prorsus irriti et frustranei.</p> <closer><salute>Vale et fave
                        <lb/>Vir omni virtutum genere ornatissime.</salute>
<dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1714-09-22">22<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> Septembris 1714</date></dateline></closer>
